1
00:00:10,110 --> 00:00:11,010
Oh, yeah!

2
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:40,370
Is this all you can do?

3
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,860
We take money, not lives.

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,730
Do you know your actions

5
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,860
almost ruined three years of our work?

6
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,980
So you've been in on this
for three years?

7
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,650
I've busted my ass

8
00:00:51,670 --> 00:00:52,540
for this for three years!

9
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,940
I didn't do it for you!

10
00:00:58,150 --> 00:00:59,730
If that's how you want to put it,
I won't argue.

11
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:29,200
[In the Name of Justice]

12
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:32,200
[Episode 21]

13
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,940
You're the one who said
the police report was wrong,

14
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:45,450
and took me to the hospital
to question Yang Zheng again.

15
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,100
You're also the one who wanted to
report it to Mr. Xu.

16
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,170
So, why won't you
sign the report I wrote?

17
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:51,130
Why won't you sign it?

18
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,060
Why won't you sign it?

19
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,260
Tell me!

20
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,010
Tell me!

21
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:57,010
Tell me why won't you sign it?

22
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,060
Fine, I'll tell you.

23
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,540
I'll tell you.

24
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:17,780
I didn't believe

25
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,260
that Yang Zheng is dead,

26
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,540
so I went to the hospital to see him.

27
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,010
Why are you here?

28
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:40,260
Mr. Xu told me Yang Zheng

29
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:43,450
changed his statement,

30
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,260
so I came to see why.

31
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:48,890
Yang Zheng

32
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,540
died.

33
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,660
So unfortunate.

34
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,780
Nice work recently.

35
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,010
You've really taken the initiative.

36
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:01,610
Captain Sun,

37
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,170
is the Criminal Investigation Unit
hiring new officers?

38
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,940
Submit a report,

39
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,660
and I'll get you transferred here.

40
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,450
We can work together from now on.

41
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,580
To be honest,

42
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:38,980
I wanted to

43
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,850
keep investigating,

44
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,660
but they transferred me
to the countryside.

45
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,540
I couldn't anymore.

46
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,290
I couldn't anymore!

47
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,540
Zijian, take a look.

48
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,410
Look at this.

49
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,290
See this?

50
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,660
These are all your phone numbers!

51
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,810
It's clear as daylight.

52
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,370
You've been involved with Wang Yu
for three years,

53
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:51,980
prior to the Wan Hai case.

54
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:52,900
What do we do now?

55
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:54,340
First thing tomorrow,

56
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,730
I'll have to give this to Li Renjun.

57
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,250
Say something!

58
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:08,020
Xie, calm down. It's not a big deal.

59
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,660
I'm perfectly calm right now.

60
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,100
Why did Li Renjun

61
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,810
ask me to look into this phone record?

62
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,660
Because he believed
he could connect it to Wang Yu,

63
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,980
which would in turn
lead to Tianlong Company,

64
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,250
and from there,

65
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,980
straight to me, Xie Hongfei!

66
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,930
Do you two even think?

67
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:23,540
All you do is eat!

68
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,460
Did you think once the case is closed,
it's all over?

69
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,340
Fools!

70
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:28,850
And you call yourself a lawyer?

71
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,290
Fool!

72
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,170
Xie,

73
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,460
