take down Wan Hai, not him.

76
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,460
So,

77
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,340
who was the one
that wanted to sue Wan Hai?

78
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,580
It was Wang Yu.

79
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,370
If something goes wrong,
they would trace it back to him.

80
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,730
They won't get you, or me.

81
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,020
Besides, Xie,

82
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,050
at this point,

83
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,290
who would be bold enough to claim
Wan Hai is not mafia?

84
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,490
Fine.

85
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,370
Fine.

86
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,610
I'll submit these call records
to the higher-ups

87
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,050
first thing tomorrow.

88
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:15,730
Mr. Chen,

89
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,810
Mr. Cheng,

90
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:21,540
