Get to the point.

307
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:14,770
A friend of mine

308
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,420
has some

309
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:22,620
legal questions

310
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,730
