330
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,330
You didn't know that?

331
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:05,900
I know.

332
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:07,660
But my friend

333
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:09,730
wants to

334
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:13,220
set the case over a decade ago.

335
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:15,980
