00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:54,330
Yeah.

352
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,010
Tell your friend

353
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:59,250
to approach this kind of question

354
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:02,250
