00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:08,290
if it needs to be
reported or overturned,

358
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:10,250
then he must do it.

359
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,860
Justice must always

360
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:13,220
take precedence.

