this coal preparation plant.

401
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:23,680
[Twenty-Eight Years Ago]

402
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:24,460
It's small,

403
00:23:25,070 --> 00:23:25,810
but rest assured,

404
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,050
my prices

405
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,810
