406
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,660
Weren't you a teacher?

407
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:32,290
How come you're doing this now?

408
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,140
I decided to change my career.

409
00:23:35,550 --> 00:23:36,490
- Kid, what are you doing?
- That took some guts.

410
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,140
I thought you finished eating.

411
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:39,730
No, we're still eating.

412
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:41,420
You little thief,

413
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,420
