414
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:43,730
I wasn't stealing!

415
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,700
You were stealing my food!
You are a thief!

416
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:50,940
What are you doing?

417
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,090
You punk,

418
