430
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:18,180
What about you? What are you doing now?

431
00:24:20,270 --> 00:24:21,290
Where do you live?

432
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:24,380
Slow down. You're gonna choke.

433
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,530
It's all yours.

434
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:26,660
Can I have a drink?

