443
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:52,530
What? What are you talking about?

444
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,050
Who are you calling a thief?

445
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:56,770
What is this?

446
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:57,460
Alright,

447
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,050
I won't fight you for the "thief" title.

448
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:00,660
But Long,

449
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,050
I still remember

450
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:04,290
how you knelt to Mr. Yu.

451
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,530
What's wrong with kneeling to Mr. Yu?

452
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,530
I owe him my life.

453
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,290
Don't say that.

454
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,860
If not for you two,

455
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,250
I'd be just

456
