to cook barbecue for.

458
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,420
Out of everyone,

459
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:25,010
Long has been with me the longest.

460
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:27,010
He took the brunt of it

