498
00:28:18,510 --> 00:28:19,050
Jiang Yuan's back

499
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:20,530
from studying overseas,

500
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:23,140
with a degree in renewable energy.

501
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,700
Having him on board

502
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:27,010
is critical

503
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:29,530
for our next move

504
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,730
into the new energy sector.

505
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:31,380
That's right.

506
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:33,010
Once we get the mine

507
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:33,900
and the land,

508
00:28:34,310 --> 00:28:37,140
we can build an EV battery plant.

509
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:38,940
Once things take off,

510
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,660
we'll bring in investors.

511
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:41,730
And then,

512
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:43,460
