527
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:08,180
Especially when he knows...

528
00:29:08,350 --> 00:29:09,620
He's nothing!

529
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:10,900
What can he do?

530
00:29:11,030 --> 00:29:12,620
I could crush him anytime!

