553
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,290
Like they say,

554
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,490
you should leave professional matters

555
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:54,050
to the experts.

556
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,570
Jiang Yuan

557
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,660
majored in new energy.

558
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,570
It's a good thing that he's willing

559
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:02,660
