561
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:05,770
Let me be clear,

562
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,730
from now on,

563
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,380
we're all on the same side.

564
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:13,140
To a win-win cooperation.

565
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,010
C'mon,

566
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:14,900
a toast.

567
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:16,490
Jiang Yuan.

568
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:21,220
Long,

569
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:23,330
what is it?

570
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,140
Sir,

571
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,220
you're about to retire.

572
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:34,730
