579
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,010
Long.

580
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:49,810
Leave,

581
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,180
now.

582
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:53,730
Chen Shenglong,

583
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:55,530
you can

584
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,860
forget about

585
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:58,180
the mine.

586
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:15,290
What's the matter with you?

587
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:17,700
Stand up straight!

588
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,180
I've told you,

589
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,730
he's the expert in new energy.

590
00:32:23,070 --> 00:32:25,220
He's our top guy in Dongping.

591
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:27,530
He's our best choice!

592
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,730
