600
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,010
have you heard nothing I've said?

601
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,090
You didn't understand anything?

602
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,140
Sir,

603
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:05,330
