- Captain Liu, wait!

635
00:35:47,070 --> 00:35:47,980
- Captain Liu!
- Captain Liu!

636
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,340
Captain Liu,

637
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,530
