641
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:54,940
No.

642
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:55,820
Wait, Captain Liu.

643
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:57,170
You could've just called.

644
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:57,780
Let's talk in the office.

645
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:58,740
We're not mining illegally.

646
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,260
