647
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,210
We always listen to you, Captain Liu!

648
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,650
Was it you who ripped off the seal?

649
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:03,690
It wasn't me, Captain Liu.

650
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:04,980
No one would dare, Captain Liu.

651
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,170
No one dares to touch it

652
