657
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:14,090
Do you know breaking a seal is illegal?

658
00:36:14,110 --> 00:36:15,380
I know. I just did it yesterday.

659
00:36:15,590 --> 00:36:16,210
It's just one day.

660
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,940
You can't break it,
not even for a second.

661
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,050
But, I just broke it.

662
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:20,210
