Captain Liu.

663
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,490
Captain Liu, you know our situation.

664
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:22,300
We had no choice.

665
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,050
Is it here?

666
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,090
Did you rip that seal or not?

667
