Take photos as evidence.

668
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,460
No, no photos, please!

669
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:27,880
No photos.

670
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:28,690
Is anyone down there?

671
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,610
No, no one's down there.

672
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:30,460
No one?

673
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:30,900
No.

674
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:31,300
Seal it.

675
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:33,420
No, please, don't do this.

676
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,050
Didn't you already seal it?

677
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:35,340
Is there anyone down there? Answer me.

678
00:36:36,070 --> 00:36:36,610
Yes.

679
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:37,340
How many?

680
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:38,300
Four or five.

681
00:36:38,590 --> 00:36:40,010
Be precise.

682
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:42,940
How many miners went down?

683
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:44,570
Twenty-one.

684
00:36:45,070 --> 00:36:45,650
Twenty-one?

685
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:46,420
Please...

686
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:47,980
Write it down, 21 people.

687
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:48,820
