688
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:50,130
Just let me finish one load.

689
00:36:50,150 --> 00:36:50,860
Can they come up?

690
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:51,780
Are they coming up?

691
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:52,460
Just one load, please.

692
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:53,050
Seal it. Now.

693
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,260
Fine…

694
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:55,900
Go tell them to come up. It's over.

695
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,490
Go now.

696
00:36:56,510 --> 00:36:57,010
Go tell them.

697
00:36:58,110 --> 00:36:58,820
Seriously!

698
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:00,820
Just my luck!

699
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:04,130
