701
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,050
Everyone quiet! Stop talking!

702
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,210
Come out! Come out!

703
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,050
Be quiet.

704
00:37:15,510 --> 00:37:16,530
The officials are here.

705
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:18,860
Captain Liu, all 21 are accounted for.

706
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:19,650
Alright.

707
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:21,050
Captain Liu, I told you
it was 21 people.

708
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:21,900
Mr. Wan,

709
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:24,650
