712
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,210
There's nothing I can do.

713
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,010
Alright?

714
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:30,010
Maybe this will

715
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:32,380
