716
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,530
Just give us a verbal warning.

717
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:34,490
It won't happen again.

718
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,650
- Listen,
- Please, sir.

719
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,980
I'm letting you off easy.

720
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,940
Next time, it might not be me
who comes here.

721
00:37:39,030 --> 00:37:40,530
Captain Liu, you know

722
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,820
our financial situation.

723
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:42,900
I've considered your own circumstances,

724
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,090
