pay this much.

725
00:37:44,110 --> 00:37:44,650
Here, look.

726
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,010
Captain Liu.

727
00:37:46,550 --> 00:37:47,490
Captain Liu, this is too much.

728
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:48,460
Please, can you help us out?

729
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,740
Pay the fine

730
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:50,860
