762
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:29,530
I didn't know you and Mr. Sun
were this close.

763
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,980
You collaborated well
on the Wan Hai case.

764
00:40:32,630 --> 00:40:34,490
We make a good team.

765
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:35,780
