when Wan Hai took it?

791
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,300
Not only did he not run,

792
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,420
he even went to

793
00:41:39,590 --> 00:41:40,460
work for Wan Hai.

794
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:42,050
Only after the assault case was closed,

795
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:43,420
which was six months later,

796
00:41:43,670 --> 00:41:45,380
did he bring it up.

797
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:46,860
What was he waiting for?

798
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:50,530
[What was Wang Yu's motive]
If Wang Yu is compromised,

799
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,740
