00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,050
But later,

803
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:00,650
Qiao Zhenxing was replaced

804
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:03,090
by another prosecutor, Xie Hongfei,

805
00:42:03,230 --> 00:42:04,780
the one you just mentioned.

806
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:07,490
He said I was dragging the case out
for too long

807
00:42:07,510 --> 00:42:09,090
and asked if I could change my lawyer.

808
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:10,170
I told him my lawyer was fine.

809
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:11,170
I didn't want to change her.

810
00:42:11,710 --> 00:42:13,570
[Wang Yu, Xie Hongfei, Cheng Zijian]
Then, just a few days later,

811
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:16,940
Zhang Wenjing was accused
of mafia connections.

812
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:19,050
I knew something wasn't adding up,

813
00:42:19,550 --> 00:42:21,360
so I had Mr. Sun look into it,

814
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:21,840
[Wang Yu, Xie Hongfei, Cheng Zijian,
Sun Fei]

815
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:23,130
and I was right.

816
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:26,210
As for Xie Hongfei,

817
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,460
he told me as long as I plead guilty,

818
00:42:28,590 --> 00:42:30,530
he can get me sentence reductions.

819
00:42:30,710 --> 00:42:31,940
A win-win.

820
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:36,040
[Wang Yu, Xie Hongfei, Cheng Zijian
Sun Fei, Wen Qin, Wan Hai]

821
00:42:53,670 --> 00:42:54,340
Mr. Wan,

822
00:42:54,550 --> 00:42:57,260
you asked me to find you some miners.

823
00:42:57,400 --> 00:42:58,690
And now that we've done the job,

824
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,380
