825
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:01,050
Yeah.

826
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:04,460
Please.

827
00:43:07,070 --> 00:43:07,900
To be honest,

828
00:43:08,710 --> 00:43:09,170
Hui,

829
00:43:10,070 --> 00:43:10,490
everyone,

830
00:43:11,230 --> 00:43:12,210
sirs,

831
00:43:13,030 --> 00:43:13,820
I really

832
00:43:16,030 --> 00:43:16,900
can't come up

833
00:43:19,150 --> 00:43:20,570
with the money right now.

834
00:43:20,590 --> 00:43:21,420
You can't do that.

835
00:43:24,550 --> 00:43:26,420
You need to figure something out, okay?

836
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,300
Please.

837
00:43:29,030 --> 00:43:29,530
Alright!

838
00:43:30,230 --> 00:43:30,940
Shut up!

839
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:32,340
How about this:

840
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:35,340
I'll rip off

841
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:37,380
that new seal,

842
00:43:38,230 --> 00:43:39,340
and you go down and get to work.

843
00:43:40,360 --> 00:43:41,940
If you bring me back ore,

844
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:43,530
I'll pay you double.

845
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:44,980
Are you in?

846
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:47,130
You mean it?

847
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:48,420
Double pay,

848
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:49,420
are you in?

849
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:50,300
Yeah.

850
00:43:50,590 --> 00:43:51,090
I believe him.

851
00:43:51,190 --> 00:43:52,900
Let's give Mr. Wan one more chance!

852
00:43:53,030 --> 00:43:54,130
- Alright!
- Yeah!

853
00:43:54,630 --> 00:43:55,690
- Yeah!
- We're in!

854
00:44:16,640 --> 00:44:20,280
♪Had it not been for you♪

855
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:24,040
♪I'd never have known how love feels♪

856
00:44:24,040 --> 00:44:29,280
♪The darker the night,
the brighter the stars shine♪

857
00:44:31,600 --> 00:44:35,240
